726002f-a.title: Queens: 214th Place - 34th Avenue
726002f-a.text:
214th Place (foreground), at the N.W. corner of Thirty-fourth Ave.,
ahowing an old house owned by H. Hicks in 1873. Steven Thomas Hicks
states his father had it eighty years ago. In 1909 it belonged to Mary
L. Weeks.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
